-- Schneider Electric Raises Full-Year Margin Target to Between 15.5% and 16%
-- B y   F r a n c o s i   d e   B e a u p u y
-- 2010-10-20T05:36:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/schneider-electric-raises-full-year-margin-target-to-between-15-5-and-16-.html
Schneider Electric SA raised its
full-year margin target to between 15.5 percent and 16 percent
of sales, up from a July target of around 15.5 percent.  The news came in an emailed statement. The target concerns
earnings before interest, taxes and amortization, as well as the
costs of integrating a unit purchased from Areva SA.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  